{"type":null,"faqId":21649,"title":"智能闹钟功能如何使用？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.33333334in;margin-left:0.25in;margin-top:0.21666667in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.008333334in;margin-left:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">功能介绍：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">智能闹钟功能可以设置一个提前提醒时间，如果您在闹钟响铃时间之前的一段时间内，处于浅度睡眠状态，荣耀手环会给您提前的闹钟提醒。如果您处于深度睡眠状态，手环不会打扰您，会在正常的闹钟时间将您叫醒。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">必要条件：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;color:black\">、确保手环和手机蓝牙连接正常。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;color:black\">、打开华为穿戴<span>APP</span>，点击左上角手环图标，进入智能闹钟菜单，如截图所示进行设置。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><img width=\"301\" height=\"481\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805343001.jpg\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0be_r0nfn.jpg\">&nbsp;<span -converted-space=\"\">&nbsp;</span><img width=\"324\" height=\"518\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805830002.jpg\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0bf_cb5pe.jpg\">&nbsp;<span -converted-space=\"\">&nbsp;</span><img width=\"310\" height=\"496\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805466003.jpg\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0c0_iiydk.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;color:black\">、设置完智能闹钟以后，从设置页面到主页面，闹钟设置才会生效。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">注意：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;color:black\">、如果您设置闹钟的时候，手环和手机蓝牙连接不正常，您的设置信息会在下次手环和手机蓝牙连接正常，重新打开<span>APP</span>同步数据的时候设置生效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\norphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;color:black\">、闹钟功能在关机后可以正常使用，活动提醒功能在关机后无法使用</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":203,"faqType":"兼容与支持","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5350","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-System-Requirements-Support","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1427334706000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":143,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环,B1,闹钟,智能闹钟","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}